{
  "stem": "24171.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forgotten all about it, how that was going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember when they came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said that the Hungarians gonna come in, that won't be good for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't do right away things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just happened when the Germans really kind of-- well, they-- I-- I really don't know the dates and the politics, how it was then when the Germans took over the real Hungarians, and-- or it was-- I know in '39, the Hungarians came in.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the Germans took over the Hungarians, like made that [INAUDIBLE] with them, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the same thing for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was in '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in '44, they took us away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In-- in between, it was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were really-- we knew that they are big anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they didn't bother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, like the officials, they were very good with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the-- it's socialization kind of like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't have, you know, like they came in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So with the Jewish people-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I put it that way, more than the peasants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Kind of-- it was kind of like appropriate with them-- to-- to socialize.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That started the winter-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] let's see, make the date '42 they took us away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was right in the beginning of '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that time when we started to wear-- I think that's when we start to wear the-- the-- the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember having it on, but not exactly the day to-- when we put it on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I know that-- that-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been in '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it's kind of too close from the taking away.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
